column3: Traffic Alert for N Cleveland Rd:
column4: Access to N Cleveland Rd from Winchester Rd (toward I-64) is shut down due to an asphalt truck on its side near I-64.
Inbound Russell Cave Rd at Hollow Creek Rd.
Inbound Winchester Rd between Patchen Wilkes Dr and Fortune Dr.
The roadway is shut down until further notice due to a collision.
